Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,0:01:52.84,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}KNIGHTS KNIGHTS KNIGHTS OF SIDONIA Ah Ah
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.35,0:02:10.18,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}星間に行く砦は唯一の安息地
