Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.27,0:02:21.39,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}KNIGHTS KNIGHTS KNIGHTS OF SIDONIA Ah Ah
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.25,0:02:26.96,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}KNIGHTS KNIGHTS KNIGHTS OF SIDONIA
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.73,0:02:34.91,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}此所へいざ集わんと 導かれしは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.16,0:02:41.20,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}志携えて 立ち向かえ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.56,0:02:47.60,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}衛り継ぐ愛と 輝け命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.96,0:02:55.56,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}果敢に進む我ら シドニアの騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.56,0:01:36.77,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}踏上征途 光芒與我們同在
